data.description: Welcome home ito the sought-after Saddleback Townhome complex! This home features a spacious and functional layout with four bedrooms (a rare find in this complex) and three bathrooms, providing ample space for comfortable living.  The heart of this home lies in its proximity to the vibrant Powers Corridor, offering a plethora of shopping and dining options just moments away. Whether you're looking for a quick bite or planning a shopping spree, the convenience of this location is unmatched.  The main level master bedroom offers dual vanities in the attached bath, two closets and plenty of space to relax and unwind. The other three large bedrooms ensure that everyone in the household has their own comfortable retreat.  Descend to the basement and discover a sprawling family room, perfect for entertaining guests, hosting movie nights, or creating a versatile space that suits your lifestyle. The possibilities are endless in this expansive area, ready to accommodate your unique preferences.  This home seamlessly combines functionality with style, offering a rare opportunity for those seeking a four-bedroom, three-bathroom haven in a desirable location. Don't miss the chance to make this Saddleback Townhome residence your own!
